cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite the accompanying paper."
type: dataset
title: "polymarket-deadline-ils: Population-Scale Deadline-ILS Scores for Polymarket"
abstract: >
  Population-scale Deadline Information Leakage Score (ILS^dl) dataset for
  Polymarket prediction markets. Covers 2,375 markets in military/geopolitical,
  regulatory, and corporate categories (volume ≥ $50K USDC), with LLM-recovered
  event dates (T_event) and ILS^dl scores computed for 90 markets using historical
  CLOB and subgraph trade data. ILS^dl measures the fraction of total price
  movement that occurred before the underlying real-world event.
authors:
